62
00:04:18,968 --> 00:04:21,528
Database DevOps brings
software engineering

63
00:04:21,568 --> 00:04:23,168
discipline into the data layer.

64
00:04:23,768 --> 00:04:28,508
That means continuous integration
from data schema versioning

65
00:04:29,228 --> 00:04:30,968
