102
00:07:08,568 --> 00:07:14,768
Those are critical because they create a
safer path from notebook to production.

103
00:07:15,328 --> 00:07:20,148
Instead of making deployment a
dramatic once-a-quarter event, you

104
00:07:20,208 --> 00:07:22,388
make it a managed, repeatable process.

105
00:07:22,928 --> 00:07:25,328
A model in a notebook
is a science project.

106
00:07:25,668 --> 00:07:29,768
A model with testing, monitoring,
rollback strategy, and

107
00:07:29,828 --> 00:07:31,588
deployment controls in a product.

108
00:07:32,088 --> 00:07:36,478
So now we get to the part where everyone
