125
00:08:47,348 --> 00:08:52,649
Auditability matters because each answer
can be traced back to the source document.

126
00:08:53,468 --> 00:08:56,348
Cost efficiency matters
because fine-tuning every

127
00:08:56,429 --> 00:08:58,168
domain variation is expensive.

128
00:08:58,899 --> 00:09:04,339
And finally, governance matters because
access controls on the data layer can

129
00:09:04,389 --> 00:09:06,959
extend into the AI response layer.

130
00:09:07,009 --> 00:09:09,269
That combination is incredibly powerful.

131
00:09:09,909 --> 00:09:16,009
It means your AI system can be smarter,
cheaper, and more accountable at the

132
00:09:16,089 --> 00:09:21,009
