win in enterprise architecture.

133
00:09:21,608 --> 00:09:22,429
That's the focus.

134
00:09:22,929 --> 00:09:28,709
Now, a phrase I really like from the
deck is, " You cannot govern what

135
00:09:28,768 --> 00:09:34,688
