165
00:11:44,937 --> 00:11:50,517
That is very different operating model
than a traditional overnight batch report.

166
00:11:50,656 --> 00:11:54,577
You're now supporting kind
of decisions in the motion.

167
00:11:55,297 --> 00:12:00,448
Now just n- not analyzing them
in hindsight after the fact.

168
00:12:00,988 --> 00:12:04,068
And yes, that means your
complete architecture choice

169
00:12:04,148 --> 00:12:05,848
